<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 07:44:35 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a47685f4caab</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这幅色彩缤纷的壁画位于第二街240号，由丹佛艺术家鲍比·马吉·洛佩兹为2025年梅肯壁画节创作。洛佩兹以其充满活力的自然灵感艺术作品闻名，他将漩涡般的色彩、野生动物和花卉细节融入大规模设计中，为周围空间注入了能量与生机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Colorful mural of a rabbit covered in vibrant flowers and foliage, surrounded by wildflowers and tall grasses on the side of a downtown building." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a47685f4caab.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 07:44:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a472392b2395</link><description>&lt;p&gt;发现了一片巨树森林。然后，又发现了一个巨树森林的博物馆。多么巧合！

红杉国家公园真是太棒了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="In the foreground a museum with sign saying Giant Forest Museum. In the background a whole bunch of trees that makes the museum look very small." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dcr/6a472392b2395.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dcr.some.pics"&gt;@dcr&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 02:51:02 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>夜行</title><link>https://some.pics/6a470e252d050</link><description>&lt;p&gt;夜行&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Night Walk" height="1280" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pmurad/6a470e252d050.jpg" width="960"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pmurad.some.pics"&gt;@pmurad&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 01:19:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>别人生日</title><link>https://some.pics/6a46fa8019b7e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;生日周！（不是我的）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Birthday week! (not mine) " height="2268" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/duggan/6a46fa8019b7e.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://duggan.some.pics"&gt;@duggan&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 23:55:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a469f9739755</link><description>&lt;p&gt;那也是。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Lavender, full bloom, in front of the evening sun." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a469f9739755.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 17:27:54 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>